# Prospect & Enrich — Elite Design System

## Design Reference
The prospect-enrich page follows the Elite Property Prospecting Dashboard design:
- Glass morphism container (max-w-[1440px], h-[90vh], rounded-[2rem])
- Mesh gradient background (prospect-enrich-mesh)
- Slate/Indigo/Emerald palette from Tailwind
- Material Symbols Outlined for icons
- Inter font family

## Key Heuristics
1. **Sidebar**: glass-sidebar, w-80, Filters header + Reset All, pinned filters (Price Range, Location, AI Score) with push_pin, unpinned with chevron_right, More Filters button
2. **Header**: Find Deals title, Import dropdown, Research with AI gradient button (indigo-purple), Search places input, Default View, Hide Filters, Search Settings
3. **Tabs**: Total | Net New | Saved — uppercase labels, indigo active state
4. **Table**: sticky thead bg-white/95 backdrop-blur, Address with location_on icon in slate circle, emerald status badges, indigo AI score circle
5. **Footer**: Showing X-Y of Z, circular page buttons, Next Page with arrow_forward

## CSS Classes (globals.css)
- `.prospect-enrich-glass` — white 92% + backdrop-blur 16px
- `.prospect-enrich-glass-sidebar` — slate-50 80%
- `.prospect-enrich-mesh` — radial gradients background
- `.prospect-enrich-scrollbar-hide` — hide scrollbar

